[12.0, "o", "\u001b[90m⏺ Skill(project-setup) loaded\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[12.5, "o", "\u001b[90m⏺ Reading codebase...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[14.0, "o", "\r\n"]
[14.5, "o", "Here's what I found in the project:\r\n\r\n"]
[14.8, "o", "- \u001b[1mNext.js 14 App Router\u001b[0m + TypeScript + Supabase + Vitest\r\n"]
[15.1, "o", "- Server component fetches tasks, client component handles UI\r\n"]
[15.4, "o", "- \u001b[1muser_id\u001b[0m on Task model suggests per-user data scoping\r\n"]
[15.7, "o", "- AGENTS.md is a blank template — nothing filled in yet\r\n"]
[16.0, "o", "- Tests directory is empty despite Vitest being configured\r\n"]
[16.5, "o", "\r\n"]
[17.0, "o", "I'll ask questions one at a time. Let's start with the product.\r\n"]
[17.5, "o", "\r\n"]
[17.7, "o", "\u001b[1m━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.0, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.2, "o", "\u001b[1mQuestion 1 — What does this app actually do?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[18.5, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.8, "o", "The README says \"task management app\" but that covers\r\n"]
[19.0, "o", "everything from a personal sticky-note replacement to\r\n"]
[19.2, "o", "a team project tracker.\r\n"]
[19.5, "o", "\r\n"]
[19.8, "o", "Who is this for — is it a \u001b[1msingle person\u001b[0m managing\r\n"]
[20.0, "o", "their own tasks, a \u001b[1msmall team\u001b[0m sharing work,\r\n"]
[20.2, "o", "or something else entirely?\r\n"]
[20.5, "o", "\r\n"]
[20.8, "o", "\u001b[33mMy recommendation:\u001b[0m Keep it single-user for MVP.\r\n"]
[21.0, "o", "The data model already points that way — but \u001b[1muser_id\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[21.2, "o", "exists with zero auth code. That's either a placeholder\r\n"]
[21.4, "o", "or a gap we need to resolve now.\r\n"]
[22.0, "o", "\r\n"]
[22.5, "o", "\u001b[36m❯\u001b[0m "]
[23.5, "o", "i"]
[23.7, "o", "t"]
[23.8, "o", "s"]
[23.9, "o", " "]
[24.0, "o", "f"]
[24.1, "o", "o"]
[24.2, "o", "r"]
[24.3, "o", " "]
[24.4, "o", "s"]
[24.5, "o", "m"]
[24.6, "o", "a"]
[24.7, "o", "l"]
[24.8, "o", "l"]
[24.9, "o", " "]
[25.0, "o", "t"]
[25.1, "o", "e"]
[25.2, "o", "a"]
[25.3, "o", "m"]
[25.4, "o", "s"]
[25.6, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[26.5, "o", "\u001b[33mGood — but that changes things.\u001b[0m If it's for teams,\r\n"]
[26.8, "o", "the user_id field needs to become team-scoped.\r\n"]
[27.0, "o", "And we need to decide: does everyone on the team\r\n"]
[27.2, "o", "see all tasks, or only their assigned ones?\r\n"]
[27.5, "o", "\r\n"]
[27.8, "o", "Before we go further — \u001b[1mwalk me through what a team\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[28.0, "o", "\u001b[1mmember actually does\u001b[0m step by step, from opening\r\n"]
[28.2, "o", "the app to completing a task.\r\n"]
[29.0, "o", "\r\n"]
[29.5, "o", "\u001b[36m❯\u001b[0m "]
[30.5, "o", "\u001b[5m▊\u001b[0m"]
